OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFace mask rules to be eased
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin Scottish schools        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Secondary school pupils in Scotland    
OL,6, will not need to wear face coverings in
OL,7, classrooms from 28 February.           
OL,9,FFirst Minister Nicola Sturgeon said    
OL,10,Fscientific advisors had backed the move
OL,11,Fas part of a phased lifting of         
OL,12,Frestrictions.                          
OL,14,FPupils will still need to wear masks in
OL,15,Fcommunal areas and when moving around  
OL,16,Finside school buildings.               
OL,18,FMs Sturgeon said it would return pupils
OL,19,Fto "a more normal experience after many
OL,20,Fmonths of sacrifice".                  
